The Middelburg Observer attained the PMR Award as a company or institution doing the most in their sector to stimulate economic growth and development in the Mpumalanga Province. It is the seventh consecutive year that the Middelburg Observer has been nominated. The winners were chosen by a panel made up of CEO’s, MD’s, business owners, company directors, managers and government officials based in Mpumalanga. PMR Africa is a consultancy and research company based in South Africa. •The purpose of their award ceremony is to create a platform where companies and institutions can be branded as entities with growing potential.